# Episode 02

## Automated Lead Routing & Warm Lead Follow-Up

### Objective

Automatically route qualified leads to the correct communication channel.

---

## What Was Built

AI Analysis

↓

IF Node

↓

Hot Lead

↓

Telegram Alert

OR

↓

Warm Lead

↓

Email Follow-Up

---

## Features

### Hot Lead Route

Condition:

Lead Temperature = Hot

Action:

Send Telegram notification.

Purpose:

Immediate sales attention.

---

### Warm Lead Route

Condition:

Lead Temperature = Warm

Action:

Send automated email.

Purpose:

Maintain communication and encourage conversion.

